  <summary>5/12/2010--Passed House amended.
Supports the goals of World TB Day to raise awareness about tuberculosis. Commends the progress made by U.S.-led anti-tuberculosis programs. Reaffirms the commitment of the House of Representatives to global tuberculosis control through the Lantos-Hyde U.S. Leadership Against HIV/AIDS, Tuberculosis and Malaria Act of 2008.</summary>
